org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.interfaces

Interface ItemDocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EntityDocument, TermedDocument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ItemDocumentImpl, JacksonItemDocument

    public interface ItemDocument
extends TermedDocument
    Interface for datasets that describe items. It extends EntityDocument with information about site links and statements.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch

      • getItemId

        ItemIdValue getItemId()
        Return the ID of the item that the data refers to. The result is the same as that of EntityDocument.getEntityId(), but declared with a more specific result type.
        Returns:
        item id

      • getStatementGroups

        List<StatementGroup> getStatementGroups()
        Return the list of all StatementGroups stored for this item. The order of StatementGroups is significant.
        Returns:
        list of StatementGroups

      • getAllStatements

        Iterator<Statement> getAllStatements()
        Returns an iterator that provides access to all statements, without considering the statement groups. The order of statements is preserved.
        Returns:
        iterator over all statements
